---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SiteHeader from "../components/SiteHeader.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service — vibs.io"
  description="The terms that govern your use of the vibs.io project planning sandbox."
>
  <SiteHeader />

  <main id="main" class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-10 sm:px-6">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Effective date: July 11, 2026</p>

    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">1. The service</h2>
        <p>
          vibs.io is a project management planning sandbox. The core workspace runs entirely in your
          browser; optional AI-powered features require signing in with a Google account. By using
          vibs.io you agree to these terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">2. Your data, your links</h2>
        <p>
          Workspace data is stored in your URL and your browser rather than on our servers. You are
          responsible for saving and sharing your workspace links appropriately. We cannot recover a
          workspace whose link and browser storage have both been lost, and we are not responsible
          for the contents of links you choose to share with others.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">3. Acceptable use</h2>
        <p>
          Don't use vibs.io to violate laws, infringe others' rights, distribute malicious content,
          or attempt to disrupt, overload, or reverse-engineer the service or its AI endpoints.
          Automated abuse of AI features may result in access being suspended.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">4. AI-generated content</h2>
        <p>
          Blueprints, task breakdowns, and forecasts are planning aids generated by statistical and
          AI systems. They may be incomplete or wrong. You own your inputs and may use the outputs
          freely, but you are responsible for reviewing them before relying on them in real projects.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">5. Accounts</h2>
        <p>
          Sign-in uses Google OAuth via Supabase. You are responsible for the security of your Google
          account. We may suspend accounts that violate these terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">6. Service availability</h2>
        <p>
          vibs.io is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We may modify, suspend, or
          discontinue features at any time. To the maximum extent permitted by law, we are not liable
          for indirect or consequential damages arising from your use of the service.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">7. Changes to these terms</h2>
        <p>
          We may update these terms as the service evolves. Material changes will be reflected by an
          updated effective date on this page. Continued use after changes means you accept the
          revised terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">8. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about these terms: <a href="mailto:silverspectrummedia@gmail.com" class="font-medium text-indigo-600 hover:underline dark:text-indigo-400">silverspectrummedia@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-10 text-sm">
      <a href="/" class="font-medium text-indigo-600 hover:underline dark:text-indigo-400">← Back to the workspace</a>
    </p>
  </main>

  <footer class="border-t border-slate-200 py-6 dark:border-slate-800">
    <p class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 text-xs text-slate-400 sm:px-6 dark:text-slate-500">
      vibs.io · <a href="/privacy" class="hover:underline">Privacy</a> · <a href="/terms" class="hover:underline">Terms</a>
    </p>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>
